snippet.title: Ragdoll Training Center - Physics Based Arcade Game
snippet.description:
COMING SOON
ADD TO WISHLIST NOW
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3127610/Ragdoll_Training_Center/

Ragdoll Training Center is a physics based arcade game where you push a ragdoll character through the map.
Avoid obstacles and reach the finish in shortets possible time.
Compete for thousandths of a second differences with other players in global ranking.
Create your own maps in Map Editor and try maps made by other players.

Discord: https://discord.gg/xJsKC2p2

Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/RagdollTrainingCenter/
FB: https://www.facebook.com/MeatyOreGames/
X: https://x.com/meatyoregames
